subject: Automobile Racing
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Matt Kenseth, with help from a teammate, held off Dale Earnhardt Jr. in an extra two-lap sprint after a series of crashes near the end of the race.
